    "Name": "Epona Pursuit Tank",
    "UIName": "Epona Pursuit Tank A",
    "Details": "<b>Name: <color=#85DBF6>Epona Pursuit Tank A</color>\nArmor: <color=#85DBF6>Ferro-Fibrous</color>\tTechnology: <color=#85DBF6>Clan</color>\nMovement: <color=#85DBF6>9/14 (Hover)</color>\tEngine: <color=#85DBF6>215 Fusion</color></b>\n\nThe Epona Pursuit Tank was once a front-line unit in the most prestigious Galaxies of the Horses. Known for its speed and scouting capabilities, it is built on the largest hovercraft frame possible, reaching 150 km/h at the expense of armor.\n\nThe second most popular configuration of the Epona carries a pair of LRM-20s in its turret. Four tons of ammunition keeps the Epona in supply through most Trials. To supplement this support variant, the A mounts paired ER Medium Lasers in the front. Next to those lasers is a TAG that enables the Epona A to call in heavy artillery support.",
